             was indicted for <rs id="t18320405-209-off1243" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18320405-209-off1243" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320405-209-off1243" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing' on the <rs id="t18320405-209-cd1244" type="crimeDate">13th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320405-209-off1243 t18320405-209-cd1244"></join>, 2 violins, value 3l. 10s., and 1 violin bow, value 3s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18320405-209-victim1840" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     King
                  <interp inst="t18320405-209-victim1840" type="surname" value="King"></interp>
